The paper deals with capacity analysis of a multi-antenna multi-user system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). It also discusses the advantages of serving only subsets of users, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and control engineering (cs.SY). The paper also provides guidelines on how many users to serve to get near-capacity performance with low complexity, which is a topic related to multimedia systems (cs.MM) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
